Class DistributedMap

java.lang.Object
  poodah.processes.utils.DistributedMap

public class DistributedMap
extends java.lang.Object

THIS IS THE BRAIN OF OUR FRAMEWORK. All the redistribution and data that is associated with each job, each file, and each worker is registered here.
